name: Crazy Nine patch Cushions made with 100% cotton hand printed and moda fabric
description:
Gorgeous 30cm cushions made with lino printed fabric from Ruby Victoria Letterpress & Printmaking and 100% cotton from Moda.

Golden Yellow, Blue and Pink 3 for $65

Envelope back - no zips to scratch your lounge!

3 match perfectly or just buy one to 'pretty up' your space!

Note - inserts WILL come with these ones as they are a unique size. I can take them out for cheaper postage. Postage will depend on location. Happy to refund if postage is cheaper

description:
Go with the Flow

name: Hungry Caterpillar Draught Stopper
description:
This adorable draught stopper has a 'sleeve' at the bottom (brown ground part) where a commercial draught snake slides in. The top (caterpillar and sun) are stuffed with toy filling. 

It is 88cm long and about 25m high at the top of the sun.
Middle photo show's it 'in action' behind a door.

Would also make a great cuddle toy (without the snake!)

Postage will depend on location - i will post WITHOUT the draught snake (can buy one in woolies) as it will make it much lighter. However, it is still reasonably bulky!  
I am really not sure what shipping for this will cost so have set it at $15 - happy to refund if it is less!
